query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_schools,
  COUNT(nameEn) as has_english_name,
  COUNT(category) as has_category,
  COUNT(gender) as has_gender,
  COUNT(religion) as has_religion,
  COUNT(language) as has_language,
  COUNT(curriculum) as has_curriculum,
  COUNT(band) as has_band,
  COUNT(schoolNet) as has_school_net,
  COUNT(linkedSchool) as has_linked_school,
  COUNT(tuitionFeeMin) as has_tuition_fee,
  COUNT(studentCount) as has_student_count,
  COUNT(teacherCount) as has_teacher_count,
  COUNT(classCount) as has_class_count,
  COUNT(foundedYear) as has_founded_year,
  COUNT(description) as has_description,
  COUNT(features) as has_features,
  COUNT(website) as has_website,
  COUNT(email) as has_email
FROM schools;
